{"tid":1012433,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，前日年初一終於收咗個閪客皮","createTime":"2019-02-07T14:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T16:56:05.000Z","uid":40569,"like":113,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"df77aec41d00c403cea6fc6f37afa64c483ec710","tid":1012433,"uid":40569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"話說本人只係一個學生，見近排新年又冇嘢做咪翻下pt，做sell屎狗囉<br />\n<br />\n因為本身呢份工已經翻咗一段時間，做嘢都幾熟手，平時已經長期企係cashier收錢(份工唔俾啲比較新嘅同事掂錢)<br />\n<br />\n點知前日大年初一啲客又黎料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見條撚樣入到黎閪口閪面咁，啲同事已經係對講機話呢個客好閪，小心啲<br />\n<br />\n咁好啦，佢揀揀揀揀撚咗成半個鐘終於揀咗件衫(特價貨)過黎埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小姐需唔需要膠袋架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （勁串咁講）要收錢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要收五毫子呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁唔要啦，你同我攞個透明袋入住佢<br />\n（平時翻貨每件衫都會有個透明袋入住，費時污漕，一般我地都會收埋啲俾啲客袋住啲衫，但我見佢咁串梗係話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思呀，我地咁啱掉曬啦，一個都冇啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你搵下啦，點會冇呀平時你地都有架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地真係冇啦，已經掉曬，你自己一眼都望到冇啦，一係你俾五毫子我加個膠袋啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你冇透明袋俾我我點拎呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快啲啦如果冇我唔買架啦<br />\n<br />\n嗰時已經心諗，屌，你買得嗰百幾蚊嘢仲咁撚多嗲，連五毫子都俾唔撚起？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好呀唔緊要我幫你退咗佢啦(已經俾咗錢，佢攞錢出黎嗰時仲要dum啲錢係枱面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n(俾翻錢佢)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你有冇病呀，叫你俾個透明袋我姐又唔俾，你識唔識做生意架，等我投訴你等你老細炒咗你<br />\n<br />\n屌，唔做佢生意咪唔做佢生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正嗰時已經一早做到當日target有錢分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好呀，咁你慢慢投訴啦，嗱，呢度係意見卡，俾埋支筆你，我叫______________呀，記得寫得清楚啲啦，唔滿意俾埋office電話你好冇？買嗰少少嘢係度嘈住曬，大年初一仲要對住你啲咁嘅客真係想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 使唔使我恭喜埋你發財呀，走啦依家唔做你生意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住見到佢塊面燶撚過舊炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後佢勁快咁寫完張意見卡走咗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實張垃圾卡公司廿年都唔收一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己仲要有鎖匙開到個箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢打電話都冇用，新年寫字樓放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢走咗之後啲同事笑撚到仆街，仲話我做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680f7e4b88e5666d4b364a1feaeaa9cfe8531077","tid":1012433,"uid":15009,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n仲夠膽開post<br />\n投訴到你仆街！<br />\n開埋你名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"